test_zero_range:
assert [1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6] == []
  Left contains 6 more items, first extra item: 1
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6]
test_large_range:
assert [] == [1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, ...]
  Right contains 7 more items, first extra item: 1
  Full diff:
  - [1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7]
  + []
test_even_range:
assert [] == [2, 4, 6, 8, 10, 12, ...]
  Right contains 7 more items, first extra item: 2
  Full diff:
  - [2, 4, 6, 8, 10, 12, 14]
  + []
